files.content:
# OUCML

[GAN](https://github.com/OUCMachineLearning/OUCML/tree/master/GAN)

大家编写README.MD文件的时候，可以参考[github上README.md文件如何编写](https://blog.csdn.net/liu537192/article/details/45693529)。

files.name: md2zh.py
files.content:
import re def repl(m): inner_word = m.group(1) return '

$' + inner_word + '$

' with open('readme.md', 'r') as f_read: text = f_read.readlines() for k, item in enumerate(text): text[k] = re.sub(r'\$\$(.*?)\$\$', repl, item) with open('zhihu.md', 'w') as f_write: f_write.writelines(text)
